# Trailing-slash 301 redirects for SEO canonicalization.
#
# Cloudflare Workers Static Assets emits HTTP 307 for trailing-slash redirects
# by default. Search engines treat 307 as temporary and repeatedly probe the
# slashed variant. These 301 rules permanently canonicalize to the no-slash form.

/schools/              /schools               301
/insights/             /insights              301
/about/                /about                 301
